### Fix 2 — Gemini Model Name

**What changed**: [lib/ai.ts](file:///j:/PaceUp/lib/ai.ts#L16) — model list updated from `gemini-1.5-pro` / `gemini-1.5-flash` to `gemini-2.5-flash` / `gemini-2.0-flash`.

**How to verify**:
1. Go to Settings → AI Keys.
2. Delete your existing Gemini key.
3. Add a new key with provider "Gemini (Google)" and model `gemini-2.5-flash`.
4. Submit a project brief → AI should successfully assign tasks (no more 404 error).

