### Fix 5 — Email From Address

**What changed**: [lib/email.ts](file:///j:/PaceUp/lib/email.ts#L8) — Now reads `RESEND_FROM_EMAIL` from environment variables. Added response logging for debugging.

> [!WARNING]
> Resend sandbox (`onboarding@resend.dev`) only delivers to **your own Resend account email**. For real email delivery to other people, you need a verified domain in Resend. This is a Resend policy, not a code issue.

