### Fix 6 — Document Upload for Brief

**New files**:
- [api/briefs/parse/route.ts](file:///j:/PaceUp/app/api/briefs/parse/route.ts) — Accepts PDF, DOCX, TXT, MD files via FormData. Uses `pdf-parse` (v2) for PDFs, `mammoth` for DOCX. Sends extracted text to the user's AI model to parse into the 4 brief fields.

**Modified files**:
- [brief/page.tsx](file:///j:/PaceUp/app/dashboard/group/[id]/brief/page.tsx) — Two-mode toggle: "Paste Text" vs "Upload Document". On upload, file is parsed → fields are populated → user reviews → submits.

**How to verify**:
1. Go to a group's Brief page.
2. Click "Upload Document" toggle.
3. Upload a PDF or DOCX file containing project information.
4. Wait for AI parsing (spinner shows) → fields auto-populate.
5. View switches to "Paste Text" mode with fields pre-filled → review and edit → submit.

